quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"And indeed We have created many jinns and men for hell; they have hearts in which their is no understanding; and the eyes they do not see with; and the ears they do not hear with; they are like cattle – in fact more astray; it is they who are the neglectful."
  7,180,"And for Allah only are the best names, so invoke Him by them; and abandon those who depart from the truth regarding His names; they will soon receive the reward of their deeds."
  7,181,"And from Our creation is a group that shows the truth and establishes justice with it."
  7,182,"And those who denied Our signs – We shall soon steadily lead them towards the punishment, from the place they will not know."
  7,183,"And I will give them respite; indeed My secret plan is extremely solid."
  7,184,"Do they not ponder that their companion is far removed from insanity? In fact he is clearly a Herald of Warning."
  7,185,"Have they not pondered deeply regarding the kingdom of the heavens and the earth, and whatever things Allah created? And that possibly their promise (of death) may have come near? So after this*, in what will they believe? (*Advent of the Last Prophet and the Holy Qur’an.)"
  7,186,"For one whom Allah sends astray, there is none to guide him; and He leaves them to wander in their rebellion."
  7,187,"They ask you about the Resurrection, as to when it is destined; say, “Indeed its knowledge is with my Lord; only He will manifest it at its time; it is proving cumbersome in the heavens and the earth; it will not come to you except suddenly”; they question you as if you have researched it deeply; say, “Indeed its knowledge is with Allah only but most people do not know.”"
